{"tid":755187,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"家英哥自嘲要阿姐供養","createTime":"2018-07-25T04:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T10:37:51.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a074c6f71824fe5279784a51aab8ae5bb1ea259","tid":755187,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:09:01.000Z","msg":"羅家英昨日在灣仔書展出席「粵劇文武生在劇團中的工作及影響力」講座。家英哥表示做文武生很慘，要一腳踢，兼要顧台前幕後、台上台下，他說：「如果冇班主，文武生要搵錢招兵買馬，蝕本就慘，呢四十幾年，我都蝕過好多次，加埋都有百幾萬。」<br />\n家英哥又說花旦如果有良心，就會收少一點酬勞。當問到太太汪明荃有否良心時，家英哥說：「有良心，初頭我畀，後來一人一半，不過都慘㗎，我出雞，佢出豉油。」他又自爆臨老做小白臉，由阿姐供養。家英哥透露下月會跟阿姐到美國，因為姪仔結婚。<br />\n採訪、攝影：黃曉妍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180724/20458191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458191&d=URtt3CCGnuGnLRHpeOfLmhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=befb0e5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458191&h=65f9d9cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180724/20458191</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180724/large/24ec2p26e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180724%2Flarge%2F24ec2p26e.jpg&h=df22b91b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d252b460826dbee086df5eccf524364f93fca94c","tid":755187,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"真男人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc2f5576db1ab55cf85fefd3ca68595dea3de28","tid":755187,"uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d252b460826dbee086df5eccf524364f93fca94c","tid":755187,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"真男人！<img src=